Reasoning: 
1. cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper deals with natural language sentence inputs to task-based dialog systems and proposes a method for OOD detection in this context.
2. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also likely as the paper proposes a machine learning approach for OOD detection.
3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is relevant as the paper proposes a likelihood ratio based approach and a generative classifier for OOD detection.
4. cs.SD (Software Engineering) is less likely but still possible as the paper deals with real-world deployment of models and proposes a method for improving model performance in this context.
5. cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) is also less likely but possible as OOD detection is relevant in the context of security and privacy.
